headline: Is Hubbell (HUBB) Pricing Look Stretched After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Hubbell's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you cut through the noise and focus on valuation. Hubbell's share price recently closed at US$522.30, with returns of 1.2% over the last 7 days, 6.7% over the last 30 days, 12.8% year to date, 34.9% over 1 year and 120.1% over 3 years, while the 5 year return sits at 218.9%.
